            <h3>Why we made this project</h3>
            <p>It's a simple team website my friend Alex and I made during <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/index.html">COVID-19</a> lockdown because 
                we wanted to help our robotics team's business group a way to promote our team. We made also because every team has a website to present to the world and we thought
            we need one as well. </p>
                
            <h3>Challenges</h3>
            <h4>Video background</h4>
            <p>I think it will be very cool and impressive if we can have a video as background.
                So I used <a href="https://developers.google.com/youtube/iframe_api_reference">YouTube API</a> to embed the video as backgorund so it looks cool on the <a href="http://team5805.robingan.org/">front page</a>. 
                The reason why I chose Youtuube API instead using <abbr>MP4</abbr> files is that MP4 takes time to load which is not good for user experience. 
            </p>
